* Dinobot reared his head back as Tavatron had transformed and snarled as 
she ran up the trail ahead of him, he shook his head and snarled...*

" Dinobot, Maximize!"

* Once transformed he made his way up the remainder of the trail and walked 
calmly past Tavatron, he then slapped the end of his tail against Tavatron's 
shoulder.*

" Show off!"

* Dinobot continued to walk in the direction of the base, not bothering to 
wait for Tavatron, besides, if she was that fast then she could just catch 
up to him.
He looked at the terrain as he walked and noticed that he was now fully 
healed and both optics worked.                                      There 
wasn't nothing more then sand and boulders for the next 67 clicks, a good 
place for a Predacon ambush!*
